When the two English forms (“{count} day” / “{count}
        days”) to four Czech forms (“{count} den”, “{count}
        dny”, “{count} dne”, “{count} dní”? Or
      Arabic (5 forms), or Chinese one form?

[ICU          MessageFormat] example: {file_count, plural,
       =0 {You deleted no file.}
       =1 {You deleted one file.}
    other {You deleted # files.}
}

